{"tid":2096982,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"知名女團Gfriend整很大！網民：驚呆了！","createTime":"2020-07-06T13:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T14:02:58.000Z","uid":34489,"like":35,"dislike":170,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"969fe890cd44fe7c1fa3ec098b5584838107b04b","tid":2096982,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:16:50.000Z","msg":"gfriend 狗朋友快要回歸了，近日概念照也一一釋出，但是眾網民看完後被驚呆了，變化真的是太大了，整容前後不敢相信是一個人，完全認不出來！<br />\n<br />\n    她們團真的臉太僵了，剛開始覺得信飛鼻子假到爆 結果現在看其實是最自然的。銀河直接就填充成了充氣人偶了。鄭藝琳同理 太嚇人了。其實我覺得她出道初期挺清純挺好的 現在是真正的充氣人偶臉了唷！面對粉絲這就尷尬了。<br />\n<br />\n    主唱宇宙不多說了 懂的都懂 回歸一次返場重修一次 換頭不知幾次了 真不擔心崩嗎。。有見及此本報派出特約記者 邊伯賢良淑德 去訪問一下網民<br />\n<br />\n網民1:個鼻全部人都一樣嘅？<br />\n<br />\n網民2:不求同年同月同日生 只求同鼻同面同醫生<br />\n<br />\n網民3:為什麼不找一間好一點的醫院呀看着太粗糙了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ai8h6ni.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAi8h6ni.png&h=bb295ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZyBCub.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZyBCub.png&h=a6f10a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BcnKMnD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBcnKMnD.png&h=5df50286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8c1WCus.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8c1WCus.png&h=30fa4e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mugC6nT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmugC6nT.png&h=879f233f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFOU8Bt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFOU8Bt.png&h=2833cc76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGfriend 真的收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad873744b3005a39545648ec4c9c538137b8856","tid":209698